description:
[If you connect the Male Lead and the Female Lead, you can return to the original world.]

I was in possession of a novel with that phrase.

“Where did she go?”

The Female Lead disappeared and did not even appear.

“…?”

The name of the villainess who will interfere with the happy ending did not even come out.

The Male Lead is struggling alone without the Female Lead.

So I tried to rescue the Male Lead first.

“Just stay beside me, never go anywhere and only go as far as I can protect you.”

The Male Lead is telling me the lines he should say to the Female Lead.

‘Can I just go back?’>
